OL,5, Daniel Thomson is homeless and has been
OL,6, "sofa surfing" for four months.        
OL,8,FHe works 50 hours a week in a chip shop
OL,9,Fbut can't find an affordable place to  
OL,10,Fstay in his home city of Glasgow.      
OL,12,FHis only option for now, according to  
OL,13,Flocal housing groups, is a spell in one
OL,14,Fof the city's homeless hostels.        
OL,16,FThe 37-year-old is one of a growing    
OL,17,Fnumber of people in Scotland described 
OL,18,Fas suffering "core homelessness" -     
OL,19,Fliving in hostels, rough sleeping or   
OL,20,Fstaying with friends.                  
